                 Leslie and Steuber, Volker and van Albada, Sacha",
  affiliation = "School of Mathematical and Statistical Sciences, Arizona State
                 University, Tempe, AZ, USA. sharon.crook@asu.edu",
  abstract    = "As computational neuroscience matures, many simulation
                 environments are available that are useful for neuronal
                 network modeling. However, methods for successfully
                 documenting models for publication and for exchanging models
