                 reconstructs retinal flat-mounts by mapping them into a
                 standard, spherical retinal space. This is achieved by:
                 stitching the marked-up cuts of the flat-mount outline;
                 dividing the stitched outline into a mesh whose vertices then
                 are mapped onto a curtailed sphere; and finally moving the
